<p>But what happens if authentication fails?</p>
<h2 id="testing-with-a-bad-token">Testing with a bad Token <a class="headerlink" href="handling-invalid-token#testing-with-a-bad-token" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>Let's find out! Copy <code>testRequiresAuthentication()</code>, paste it, and rename it to
<code>testBadToken()</code>:</p>
